reviewText: I DO NOT KNOW WHAT THE SELLER OF THIS DVD IS THINKING .WHO GONNA PAY THE PRICE OF A NEW HOUSE FOR A ROUND PEICE OF PLASTIC. SOME REALLY BIG IS DEFINITELY WRONG HERE.

This is a waste of money. the cover art photo is not part of the five minute feature in which linda stars. the transfer is overexposed and out of focus. Not worth the time it takes to watch. They then fill in the rest with overexposed and out of focus swedish erotica loops. terrible
